The Native American Center sponsors http://nas.ucdavis.edu/NALC/home.html language projects that bring UC Davis into direct contact with Indian communities through a variety of revitalization and research projects.  The centers professors, postdocs, and grad students cunduct research on a number of languages, including Luiseño, Juaneño, Nisenan, Cherokee, Yukatek Maya, Nahuatl, Otomí, and Miwok.

